OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCanada reaches $31bn deal  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin indigenous child welfare
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcase                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Canada has announced C$40bn ($31bn;    
OL,6, #23.6bn) in compensation for indigenous
OL,7, children and families harmed by the    
OL,8, on-reserve child welfare system.       
OL,10,FIt's the largest class-action          
OL,11,Fsettlement in Canadian history.        
OL,13,FThe agreements-in-principle, announced 
OL,14,Fon Tuesday, sets aside funds for both  
OL,15,Fcompensation and reforms.              
OL,17,FIn 2016, a tribunal ruled that Canada  
OL,18,Fhad underfunded First Nations          
OL,19,Fchildren's services compared with those
OL,20,Ffor non-indigenous children.           
